PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779350762
OL,3,CSouthampton fans demand money back and
OL,4,Canswers after 'spygate'
OL,6,FSouthampton FC fans are calling for
OL,7,Fanswers and their money back, saying
OL,8,F'spygate' has left them them "totally
OL,9,Fridiculed".
OL,11,FThe club has apologised to supporters
OL,12,Fover the scandal, which left them
OL,13,Fexpelled from the Championship Play-
OL,14,Foff final at Wembley this weekend.
OL,16,FSouthampton FC were not only found to
OL,17,Fhave spied on Middlesbrough earlier
OL,18,Fthis month, but also Oxford United in
OL,19,FDecember 2025 and Ipswich Town in
OL,20,FApril 2026.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779350762
OL,3,CSouthampton fans demand money back and
OL,4,Canswers after 'spygate'
OL,6,FRuss Kitching has been supporting the
OL,7,Fclub since 1969 and said he's "never
OL,8,Fknown anything like this" in his life,
OL,9,Fand it has left him "gutted".
OL,11,FHe said: "We feel totally ridiculed.
OL,12,FSome fans, they spend their whole
OL,13,Fentire income on following the Saints,
OL,14,Fas they do any other football club,
OL,15,Fand no one's thinking of the fans
OL,16,Fhere. It's a really bad situation.
OL,18,F"I think we should demand our money
OL,19,Fback, the season ticket holders.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779350762
OL,3,CSouthampton fans demand money back and
OL,4,Canswers after 'spygate'
OL,6,F"I want to put forward that #1500 per
OL,7,Fseason ticket holder is refunded back
OL,8,Fto every single member. Those that
OL,9,Fhave travelled on the playoffs needs
OL,10,Fto be reimbursed for their travel. And
OL,11,Fif they're flashing the cash out
OL,12,Fthere, give it back to the fans, and
OL,13,Fthat's what we want to see."
OL,15,FSaints fan Dowayne Neufville used to
OL,16,Fcoach for the club and had tickets for
OL,17,Fthe playoffs at Wembley. He said he's
OL,18,Fmassively disappointed and that
OL,19,F'spygate' has tarnished the club's
OL,20,Freputation, describing the situation
OL,21,Fas "surreal".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779350762
OL,3,CSouthampton fans demand money back and
OL,4,Canswers after 'spygate'
OL,6,F"Not only have we been punished but
OL,7,Fit's probably the worst possible
OL,8,Fpunishment as well. And then I'm
OL,9,Fracking through my brain and I'm
OL,10,Fthinking do we deserve it, what's the
OL,11,Fsituation, why is this happening etc.
OL,13,F"I'll be honest, we do deserve it.
OL,15,F"I don't want it to be a fact, but it
OL,16,Fis a fact.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779350762
OL,3,CSouthampton fans demand money back and
OL,4,Canswers after 'spygate'
OL,6,F"We're a club that has been built off
OL,7,Fof talent, hard work, determination,
OL,8,Fgrit and you know we've produced world
OL,9,Fclass players throughout the years.
OL,10,FAnd then to have this tarnishing our
OL,11,Freputation, you know, we need answers.
OL,13,F"As fans, we need answers. Serious
OL,14,Fanswers."
OL,16,FWith the side not travelling to
OL,17,FWembley this weekend, it's dashed
OL,18,Ftheir hopes of promotion to the
OL,19,FPremier League next season.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779350762
OL,3,CSouthampton fans demand money back and
OL,4,Canswers after 'spygate'
OL,6,FMiddlesbrough are now set to take on
OL,7,FHull in Saturday's play-off final
OL,8,Finstead - but Southampton are
OL,9,Fappealing.
OL,11,FAnd fans are mixed over how they're
OL,12,Freferring to the ruling - some call it
OL,13,F"cheating" while others are hesitant
OL,14,Fto give it that label.
OL,16,FRuss Kitching said: "We can take
OL,17,Freceivership, we can take relegation
OL,18,Fbut this is cheating. And it's a kick,
OL,19,Fit's so bad."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779350762
OL,3,CSouthampton fans demand money back and
OL,4,Canswers after 'spygate'
OL,6,FDerek Crouch had paid #65 to go to
OL,7,FWembley and said the team should be
OL,8,Fpunished, but that it should come as a
OL,9,Ffine or a point deduction, and the
OL,10,Fclub should still be allowed in the
OL,11,Fplay-offs.
OL,13,F"We was all looking forward to going
OL,14,Fback up London, Wembley again for the
OL,15,Fsecond the time this year. And we just
OL,16,Fcan't believe it. You can't.
OL,18,F"All this fuss with Middlesborough
OL,19,Fmoaning about it, all that. We beat
OL,20,Fthem fair and square and we should be
OL,21,Fthere, you know.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779350762
OL,3,CSouthampton fans demand money back and
OL,4,Canswers after 'spygate'
OL,6,F"We didn't cheat to get there. We
OL,7,Fdidn't cheat at all."
OL,9,FRichard Shelley has been a fan for 53
OL,10,Fyears. He says he had tickets for
OL,11,FSaturday and is very sad that he won't
OL,12,Fbe able to make more memories at
OL,13,FWembley.
OL,15,FHe says those memories have now been
OL,16,F"taken away" from him and many other
OL,17,FSaints fans.
OL,19,FHe said: "Cheating's a very strong
OL,20,Fword, but it's hard to argue in this
OL,21,Fsituation, I think.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779350762
OL,3,CSouthampton fans demand money back and
OL,4,Canswers after 'spygate'
OL,6,F"We broke some rules and regulations.
OL,7,FIs that cheating? You could argue it
OL,8,Fis or isn't, but it's just the
OL,9,Fridicule that's now on social media
OL,10,Fand other fans.
OL,12,FHe added that he is seriously
OL,13,Fconsidering not renewing his season
OL,14,Fticket next year, and that a lot will
OL,15,Fdepend on how the club react to what's
OL,16,Fhappened in the last few weeks, and
OL,17,Fhow they start to "build those bridges
OL,18,F- not just with Saints fans, but I
OL,19,Fthink football in general."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779350762
OL,3,CSouthampton fans demand money back and
OL,4,Canswers after 'spygate'
OL,6,FMr Shelley added: "We've tarnished the
OL,7,Fname of our national sport."
OL,9,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FSouthampton did not respond to a
OL,15,Frequest for comment over season ticket
OL,16,Frefunds, but in a statement posted on
OL,17,FWednesday (20 May), Southampton's
OL,18,FChief Executive Phil Parsons
OL,19,Fapologised to the team's fans, and to
OL,20,Fthe other clubs involved.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779350762
OL,3,CSouthampton fans demand money back and
OL,4,Canswers after 'spygate'
OL,6,FHe said: "What happened was wrong.
OL,8,F"The club has admitted breaches of EFL
OL,9,FRegulations 3.4 and 127. We are sorry
OL,10,Fto the other clubs involved, and most
OL,11,Fof all to the Southampton supporters
OL,12,Fwhose extraordinary loyalty and
OL,13,Fsupport this season deserved better
OL,14,Ffrom the club.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779350762
OL,3,CSouthampton fans demand money back and
OL,4,Canswers after 'spygate'
OL,6,F"We have provided our full co-
OL,7,Foperation to the EFL's investigation
OL,8,Fand disciplinary process. Following
OL,9,Fthe appeal, we will also be writing to
OL,10,Fthe EFL to volunteer our participation
OL,11,Fin a working group on the practical
OL,12,Fapplication and enforcement of
OL,13,FRegulation 127 across the
OL,14,FChampionship. Contrition without
OL,15,Fchange is hollow, and we intend to
OL,16,Fdemonstrate change.
OL,18,F"Our appeal will be heard today, and
OL,19,Fwe will provide a further update in
OL,20,Fdue course."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
